MOVIE DETAILS

Dom Cobb (Leonardo DiCaprio) is a thief with the rare ability to enter people's dreams and steal their secrets from their subconscious. His skill has made him a hot commodity in the world of corporate espionage but has also cost him everything he loves. Cobb gets a chance at redemption when he is offered a seemingly impossible task: Plant an idea in someone's mind. If he succeeds, it will be the perfect crime, but a dangerous enemy anticipates Cobb's every move.

DIRECTED BY CHRISTOPHER NOLAN

BLOGS : learning science and pseudo-science through movie

WHY I CHOSE THIS MOVIE

This movie was chosen because it is mainly a fictional movie that talks about the idea of entering one's dreams and manipulating them. Of course, if we think about it in reality, we are far from doing that. BUT !!! We should explore the science behind dreams and try to figure in terms of biology if this is even possible !

THE THEME

Scientific aspect has been divided into exploring REM sleep in context with the movie and the science of dreaming. Furthermore, we analysed sudden Jerks During sleep. To assess Pseudoscience the blog titled dream interpretation and manipulation  extends further into such concepts. Several articles have been used to explore these topics further and have been linked  in the blogs below.
